title: My Busy Kitchen - Alex Hollywood (epub) [MentalZero]
description:
Alex Hollywood - wife of the Great British Bake Off judge Paul - reveals her simple-to-make recipes in her first cookbook My Busy Kitchen: A Lifetime of Family Recipes.

 From quick and easy midweek family meals to slow and sensational showstoppers (that are still easy to prepare!) for the weekend, Alex provides a hand-picked selection of recipes to feed all the family.

 Believing that cooking and food are all about enjoyment, Alex provides recipes that are easy and inexpensive yet a little different... with a French grandma, a Norwegian great grandmother and a father who grew up in Spain, she uses all these culinary influences to provide recipes to tickle your taste buds!

 If the recipes are good enough for Paul Hollywood - a man we all know to have high standards when it comes to food - they're sure to quickly become kitchen staples with all the family!
